name: EVA GUNDAM 02
description:
Evangelion Unit 02 is the third completed Evangelion Unit, and the first Production Model.
The unit was created as a weapon to combat the Angels, and is piloted by the Second Children, Asuka Langley Soryu.
EVA-02 was created at the NERV Third Branch located in Germany and designated as the Production Model.
My tribute to this great character.
